 skin of one tormented in Hell)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became thoroughly burned:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see Kur iv. 59.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an ulcer or the like)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became ripe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suppurated."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["Msb"]}]}}